Reverend Mother Prava requires me to complete a pilgrimage and be judged by Inarius before she grants me the blessing necessary to travel beyond the Black Lake and pursue Lilith.
I brought the cleansed Idol of the Faithful to the Shrine of the Penitent. I must speak with Vigo to learn what I must do next.
Speak with Vigo

I have begun the pilgrimage to the Shrine of the Penitent. I must bring the Idol of the Faithful to a series of shrines and read from their parchments to cleanse the idol of its curse.
